WEBVTT

00:00:58.170 --> 00:01:00.014
How are you doing?

00:01:01.768 --> 00:01:05.411
Bill Gates: I think this is
an unprecedented,

00:01:05.435 --> 00:01:08.003
really disconcerting time for everyone,

00:01:08.027 --> 00:01:10.046
with things being shut down,

00:01:10.070 --> 00:01:13.219
not knowing exactly
how long it's going to last,

00:01:13.243 --> 00:01:16.177
worrying about the health
of all the people we care about.

00:01:17.974 --> 00:01:20.911
You know, I'm lucky
that I get to connect up

00:01:20.935 --> 00:01:24.061
with video conferencing using Teams a lot,

00:01:24.085 --> 00:01:27.233
so the Foundation is stepping up

00:01:27.257 --> 00:01:32.601
and there's a lot of great people
trying to help with this crisis.